data.name: label12.Text
data.value: - Right click 'EZE' and look for 'Rebuild', but before hitting 'Rebuild' button, close first the EZE Application - Once EZE Application is closed, press the 'Rebuild' button and wait for the message if it is successfully rebuilt

data.name: label9.Text
data.value: - Find the location of the file.nupkg you've downloaded - In the Package Manager Console, Type Install-Package C:\FileLocation\NameOfNupkgFile e.g. Install-Package C:\Users\jelor\Downloads\z.dapper.plus.3.0.2.nupkg - Then hit enter button - Wait until it finished installing, then close the Package Manager Console

data.name: label28.Text
data.value:
- The sections showing in the schedules menu are linked to the sections in the student database. For example, if you remove a section in student database, the same section will be deleted in the schedules tab. And if that tab contains a schedule for that section, that will also be deleted
- If you remove a section in the student database, all information saved there will also be deleted. So always backup the information using the export feature to prevent data loss.
